Add AtomLayout and Residues classes for structure representation
- Implemented AtomLayout class to manage atom layouts with fixed shapes. - Created Residues class to handle residue metadata including deprotonation and SMILES strings. - Added utility functions for converting between atom layouts and structures. - Introduced gather indices computation for translating between layouts. - Updated tests for protein model tokenization and embedding generation to validate new structures. - Configured VSCode settings for pytest integration. - Added initial tools module for future utility functions.

fix: update submodule reference for DNA-Flex
feat: add submodules for alphafold3 and DNA-Flex integration

feat: Add DNA flexibility analysis and prediction module
- Introduced FlexibilityAnalyzer class for analyzing DNA flexibility based on structure and sequence. - Implemented methods for calculating base step parameters, predicting flexibility scores, and identifying flexible regions.
feat: Implement DNA sequence analysis module
- Created analyze function to calculate base composition, GC content, and local structural stability scores. - Added helper function for calculating stability scores based on a simple nearest-neighbor model.
feat: Implement DNA structure parsing and modification handling
- Developed DnaParser class for parsing DNA structures from PDB/mmCIF files. - Added functionality for applying modifications to DNA residues.
feat: Introduce core DNA molecule structure handling
- Created DnaAtom, DnaResidue, DnaChain, and DnaStructure classes for representing DNA structures. - Implemented methods for adding chains, calculating center of mass, and radius of gyration.
feat: Add DNA drug binding prediction module
- Developed BindingAnalyzer class for predicting DNA-drug binding sites based on sequence and structural features.
feat: Implement DNA molecular dynamics simulation module
- Created MolecularDynamics class for simulating DNA dynamics with basic thermal fluctuations and energy calculations.
feat: Add DNA sequence generation and variation module
- Developed DnaGenerator class for generating sequence variants through mutations and scoring based on similarity and stability.
feat: Implement DNA mutation effects analysis module
- Introduced MutationAnalyzer class for analyzing the effects of mutations on DNA sequences, including hotspot identification and context effects.
feat: Add DNA sequence pattern analysis using NLP techniques
- Created SequenceNLP class for analyzing DNA sequences using k-mer analysis, motif finding, and complexity measures.
